g todays knowledge workers guan li xin li xue by li wei te book  edition published in  in chinese and held by  worldcat member libraries worldwide design of corporate planning systems  development of a design framework and its application to a specific setting by homa bahrami book  editions published in  in english and held by  worldcat member libraries worldwide the emerging flexible organization  perspectives from high technology firms by homa bahrami book  edition published in  in english and held by  worldcat member libraries worldwide supplemental required materials for ba   the corporation and the international business environment book  edition published in  in english and held by  worldcat member libraries worldwide organizational structures of high technology firms  the bimodal form by homa bahrami book  edition published in  in english and held by  worldcat member libraries worldwide the empiricist mode of strategymaking in high technology firms by homa bahrami book  edition published in  in english and held by  worldcat member libraries worldwide strategic management in hightechnology firms  an exploratory study by homa bahrami book  edition published in  in english and held by  worldcat member library worldwide flexible recycling and hightechnology entrepreneurship by homa bahrami  edition published in  in english and held by  worldcat member library worldwide human resource leadership in knowledgebased entities  shaping the context of work by homa bahrami  edition published in  in english and held by  worldcat member library worldwide the corporation and the international business environment book  edition published in  in english and held by  worldcat member library worldwide the emerging flexible organization  perspectives from silicon valley by homa bahrami  edition published in  in english and held by  worldcat member library worldwide stratocracy in hightechnology firms by homa bahrami  edition published in  in english and held by  worldcat member 